インタフェースの使用
org.interledger.InterledgerPacket

  • InterledgerPacketを使用しているパッケージ 
    パッケージ 説明
    org.interledger
    The main package for top-level Interledger objects.
    org.interledger.codecs
    This package holds all codecs for the Interledger project, including top-level interfaces and abstract classes that can be utilized to create more specific codecs, such as for ASN.1 OER, JSON, Protobuf, and more.
    org.interledger.ilp
    This package contains classes related to the core Interledger Protocol (ILP) which is the foundational protocol in the overall Interledger suite of protocols.
    org.interledger.ilqp
    This package contains classes related to the Interledger Quoting Protocol (ILQP) which is one protocol in the overall Interledger suite of protocols.

      修飾子とタイプ インタフェースと説明
      interface  QuoteByDestinationAmountRequest
      A request for a quote that specifies the amount to deliver at the destination address.
      interface  QuoteByDestinationAmountResponse
      A quote sent in response to a request of type QuoteByDestinationAmountRequest.
      interface  QuoteBySourceAmountRequest
      A request for a quote with a fixed source amount to determine the destination amount.

      A quote sent in response to a request of type QuoteBySourceAmountRequest.
      interface  QuoteLiquidityRequest
      A request to receive liquidity information between the current ledger and the destination account.
      interface  QuoteLiquidityResponse
      A response to a quote request with liquidity information regarding transfers between the current ledger and the destination account.

      A parent interface for all quote requests in ILQP.
